e":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府就可以強制用安心出行，填紙太兒戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾機會政府了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"中計了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359d2e81ad0c4cd77ff570c5bc5a6998a337b9fd","tid":2424154,"uid":264362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hsfx9fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsfx9fd.jpg&h=4cd0c896&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59f39f4f3f58ad13bc2c9ce5994c17da791865f7","tid":2424154,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTS04HT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTS04HT.jpg&h=0d379f23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76d890fbe549c4f7e00f07e5ddc969ae4704f8a7","tid":2424154,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rvaVoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rvaVoO.jpg&h=3d235219&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9de77b222f31874b841e2dddd6782c6987e976a8","tid":2424154,"uid":155430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b47b6ff13f1e49650891799908e3954e6d43e21","tid":2424154,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 政府就可以強制用安心出行，填紙太兒戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾機會政府了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"安心出行都無用，咪又係無通知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425436&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=fcd9de7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425436&h=f406ca11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425436</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】對於部分近日到過名潮食館的食客收不到安心出行程式通知，創新及科技局局長薛永恒解釋，程式並無功能通知市民要接受強制檢測，只會通知跟確診者同時段在餐廳的食客。<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局局長薛永恒：「確診者同樣大約時段到過地方才會收到通知，但現在強制檢測時間是超越這個時間的，後了數天，於是部分需要強制檢測的朋友，雖然下載了安心出行，都未必有這個通知。是否需要將安心出行設計理念，擴展至強制檢測時間，做一個檢測通知，而非感染風險通知，這個可以討論。」"},{"pid":"6c957c20019494072efd63c8b9f87c65dab8d989","tid":2424154,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"香港已經輸咗"},{"pid":"4d87a6dfe82b5f86b0c13017b4cce4f0b9576843","tid":2424154,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T01:20:43.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心早前曾表示，估計名潮食館爆疫源頭為該食肆一名清潔員工，涉及一名72歲男子，居於秀茂坪邨秀康樓，他於本月14日曾做病毒檢測，當時結果沒有確診，其後於18日出現咳嗽病徵，翌日仍有上班至下午4時。"}]}